trans-unit.source: Use this class to write events.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne klassen til å skrive hendelser.

trans-unit.source: To consume events written using the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventProvider.WriteEvent%2A> and <xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventProvider.WriteTransferEvent%2A> methods, the events must be defined in a manifest; events written using the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventProvider.WriteMessageEvent%2A> method do not require a manifest.
trans-unit.target: Å bruke hendelser som er skrevet med den <xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventProvider.WriteEvent%2A>og <xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventProvider.WriteTransferEvent%2A>metoder, hendelsene må være definert i et manifest; hendelser som er skrevet med den <xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventProvider.WriteMessageEvent%2A>metoden krever ikke noe manifest.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventProvider.WriteMessageEvent%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventProvider.WriteTransferEvent%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventProvider.WriteEvent%2A>

trans-unit.source: Events can contain the following managed data types: - bool - Boolean - byte - char - decimal - double - float - Guid - int - IntPtr - long - sbyte - short - string - uint - UInt64 If an event in your manifest uses the `Boolean` in-type, you cannot write the data element using a `Boolean` data type in your managed code.
trans-unit.target: Hendelser kan inneholde følgende forvaltet datatyper: - bool - boolsk - byte - char - decimal - doble - float - Guid - int - IntPtr - lang - sbyte - kort - streng - uint - UInt64 Hvis en hendelse i din manifestet bruker den `Boolean` i type, kan du skrive data-elementet ved hjelp av en `Boolean` datatypen i behandlet kode.

trans-unit.source: The `Boolean` in-type in your manifest expects a 4-byte value, and a `Boolean` data type in managed code is 1-byte.
trans-unit.target: Den `Boolean` i typen i din manifestet forventer en 4-byte-verdi, og en `Boolean` datatypen i behandlet kode er 1-byte.

trans-unit.source: Instead, you must use an `int` data type to write the value.
trans-unit.target: I stedet må du bruke en `int` datatype ikke skrive verdien.

trans-unit.source: If you want to log a `Boolean` value, use the UInt8 in-type in your manifest.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil logge en `Boolean` verdi ved å bruke UInt8 i typen i din manifestet.

trans-unit.source: Instead, access the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.CorrelationManager%2A> property to get the <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager> object.
trans-unit.target: I stedet tilgang til den <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.CorrelationManager%2A>til å hente den <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager>objektet.</xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.CorrelationManager%2A>

trans-unit.source: Then, set the <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.ActivityId%2A> property to the activity ID.
trans-unit.target: Angi deretter <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.ActivityId%2A>egenskapen aktivitets-ID.</xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.ActivityId%2A>

trans-unit.source: You must also set the `relatedActivityId` to a <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.ActivityId%2A> value.
trans-unit.target: Du må også angi den `relatedActivityId` til en <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.ActivityId%2A>verdi.</xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.ActivityId%2A>

trans-unit.source: An instance of <xref href="System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventDescriptor"></xref> that identifies the event to write.
trans-unit.target: En forekomst av <xref href="System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventDescriptor"> </xref> som identifiserer hendelsen å skrive.

trans-unit.source: Activity identifier from the previous component.
trans-unit.target: Aktivitets-ID fra den forrige komponenten.

trans-unit.source: Use this parameter to link your component's events to the previous component's events.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne parameteren til å koble til komponent hendelser til den forrige komponenten hendelser.

trans-unit.source: An array of objects that contain the event data to write.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av objekter som inneholder Hendelsesdata for å skrive.

trans-unit.source: The data must be in the order specified in the manifest.
trans-unit.target: Dataene må være i rekkefølgen som angis i manifestet.

trans-unit.source: The array is limited to 32 objects, of which only eight may be strings.
trans-unit.target: Matrisen er begrenset til 32-objekter som kanskje bare åtte strenger.

trans-unit.source: The maximum data size for the event is limited to 64 KB minus the size of the event headers.
trans-unit.target: Den maksimale datastørrelsen for hendelsen er begrenset til 64 KB minus størrelsen på hendelse-hodene.

trans-unit.source: The event size is less if the session's buffer size is less and the session includes extended data items with the event.
trans-unit.target: Hendelsen er mindre om øktpåloggingen bufferstørrelsen er mindre og økten inkluderer utvidede dataelementer for hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: Is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the event is written; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Er <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref> om hendelsen er skrevet; ellers, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: If false, call the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventProvider.GetLastWriteEventError*> method to determine the cause of the failure.
trans-unit.target: Hvis false, kaller den <xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventProvider.GetLastWriteEventError*>metode for å finne årsaken til feilen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventProvider.GetLastWriteEventError*>

trans-unit.source: If eventPayload contains too many objects or strings.
trans-unit.target: Hvis eventPayload inneholder for mange objekter eller strenger.

trans-unit.source: Links events together when tracing events in an end-to-end scenario.
trans-unit.target: Kobler hendelser når sporing hendelser i en komplett scenarioet.

trans-unit.source: The event data is specified as a block of memory.
trans-unit.target: Hendelsesdata er angitt som en blokk minne.

trans-unit.source: The method uses the activity ID set in the thread context to identify this component.
trans-unit.target: Aktivitets-ID som er angitt i konteksten tråd brukes til å identifisere denne komponenten.

trans-unit.source: To set the activity ID, call the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventProvider.SetActivityId%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil angi aktivitets-ID, kan du kalle den <xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventProvider.SetActivityId%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.EventProvider.SetActivityId%2A>
